{"tid":1179812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左6月9日反送中遊行，6月2號都係個大日子","createTime":"2019-05-31T11:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T12:02:18.000Z","uid":186294,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5817654db212e35f176c9463c848aaa8629a988","tid":1179812,"uid":186294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"除左focus喺反送中條例之外，提提大家，要喺6月2 日前更新或確認選民資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論你有冇改名、有冇搬屋，都記住要上選民資料網上查閱系統，睇下自己仲係咪合資格選民！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳送門:​ <a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F%E2%80%8B&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=40220744\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/​</a><br />\n<br />\n事緣係我住左喺屋企23年都冇搬過屋，但3月時突然收倒選舉事務署既信，叫我確認登記地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫我如果搬左屋就提供新住址證明，如果冇搬屋，就簽佢張表格再寄返去選舉事務署。<br />\n如果唔回覆就當我冇確認自己個地址，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會取消選民資格</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3月收倒封信時我唔喺香港，家人又冇拆，4月中又寄多次黎我先拆信，再拿拿臨填佢張表格寄返去選舉事務署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家一定要上佢個網check一次，再諗下有冇信未拆未覆，我估選舉事務署係抽查下D選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你改左名、搬左屋，記住要喺6月2日前上選舉事務署個網更新選民資料呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/change.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fchange.html&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=9409508d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/change.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今年11月就係區議會選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未登記做選民既7月2號前都可以登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4fbf5fef90389471c92187b61c39db8536e0f0","tid":1179812,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1081e2328a30c05b59d25c62dfe6f0ebb6a74c69","tid":1179812,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"更新完又點?<br />\n反正做咩都冇撚用架啦, 包括投票<br />\n應該學我, 直頭取消埋選民登記, 咩都唔撚洗煩<br />\n連收信既力氣都慳返"},{"pid":"920bfb37179000ade95e41c3fc75c96404da2a80","tid":1179812,"uid":144174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}